column168:
Bio: Vronsky, P. states she was born in Burlington, Vermont & moved to New Brunswick, NJ when she was 16. Most other sources say she was born in New Brunswick. So far no birth or death record found. According to her confession, Lydia was born near the town of Burlington, NJ.                              
Family: Raised by uncle until she was 16 and then lived with her brothers in New Brunswick.
Killed after being parolled for murder
